Managing Binary Files 

bin_file.h: Basic data structure and couple of defines
bin_write.c: Used to create a binary file of data
bin_cat.c: Simply displays the content of binary file
bin_update.c: Allows us to update, in place, a value in the binary file 
bin_add.c: Adds a new record to the end of the binary file 
Make file: Manages our build process 